headline: Holland America Line's 2027-2028 Australia, New Zealand and South Pacific Season Features Deep Exploration from The Great Barrier Reef to Fiji
summary: With longer cruises and new overnight stays in Australia and Fiji, Holland America Line launched its 2027-2028 Australia, New Zealand and South Pacific season. These itineraries, ranging from 14 to 35 days, promise deep immersion in the region's wonders, from vibrant coral reefs to dramatic volcanoes and bucket-list destinations like Bora Bora and New Zealand's Bay of Islands.

headline: Viking Holdings (VIK) Q3 Earnings and Revenues Top Estimates
summary: Viking (VIK) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of +0.84% and +0.05%, respectively, for the quarter ended September 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
